API notes:
protocol_send_message (message*) - send a msg to the opposite site
add_timer - set a timer and its handler for an event related to a filedecriptor
add_read_fd - add a file descriptor to the global list of fds to select()
start_script - run a script and hang the pipe into the list of fds to select()
